The MEISD dataset contains textual, audio and visul information of the utterances in a dialogue.

The MEISD_text.csv file contains the textual utterances.
This file also comprises of the Series, season and episode numbers of the different TV series of the utterance.
The dialog ids and utterances ids are also provided.
The annotations of the sentiment, emotions and the corresponding intensity is also given for every utterance in the MEISD_text.csv file.

The audio features are given in the AUDIO FEATURES folder.
Similarly, the video features are given in the VIDEO FEATURES folder.


PLEASE cite our work, in case you intent to use the dataset for your work.
@inproceedings{firdaus2020meisd,
  title={MEISD: A Multimodal Multi-Label Emotion, Intensity and Sentiment Dialogue Dataset for Emotion Recognition and Sentiment Analysis in Conversations},
  author={Firdaus, Mauajama and Chauhan, Hardik and Ekbal, Asif and Bhattacharyya, Pushpak},
  booktitle={Proceedings of the 28th International Conference on Computational Linguistics},
  pages={4441--4453},
  year={2020}
